msgctxt "253	304"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr "¿Qué?"

msgctxt "309	378"
msgid "You didn't finish the job?"
msgstr "¿No lograste matarlo?"

msgctxt "414	485"
msgid "That's not like you in the slightest."
msgstr "Eso no es algo que harías."

msgctxt "529	589"
msgid "I have no excuse, sir."
msgstr "Le pido disculpas."

msgctxt "601	720"
msgid "I take it you let your feelings\\nget the better of you?"
msgstr "¿Acaso dejaste que tus\\nsentimientos te controlaran?"

msgctxt "811	871"
msgid "No matter."
msgstr "Bueno, no importa."

msgctxt "877	1002"
msgid "Letting a simple brat like Kido live\\nwon't make any difference in the end."
msgstr "Dejar vivir a un simple matón como Kido\\nno hará ninguna diferencia al final."

msgctxt "1024	1144"
msgid "And thanks to Kazuma Kiryu's\\ndismantling of the Ueno Seiwa..."
msgstr "Y ahora Kiryu Kazuma terminó\\ndestruyendo a Ueno Seiwa."

msgctxt "1162	1276"
msgid "Our only issue now is the money."
msgstr "Nuestro único problema es el dinero."

msgctxt "1309	1361"
msgid "The money, sir?"
msgstr "¿Dinero?"

msgctxt "1366	1422"
msgid "Correct."
msgstr "Correcto."

msgctxt "1456	1543"
msgid "You returned this file safe and sound."
msgstr "El archivo fue recuperado con éxito."

msgctxt "1602	1773"
msgid "But I wonder. Why didn't you bring\\nthe hundred billion back as well?"
msgstr "Pero, ¿por qué dejaste los\\ncien billones en ese lugar?"

msgctxt "1791	1870"
msgid "It would have been a simple enough task."
msgstr "Pudiste haberte llevado el dinero de haberlo querido."

msgctxt "1881	1973"
msgid "Especially with my men on the force assisting you."
msgstr "Con ayuda de la policía, hubiera sido una tarea sencilla."

msgctxt "2021	2100"
msgid "And yet you did nothing."
msgstr "Sin embargo, no lo hiciste."

msgctxt "2156	2249"
msgid "You never instructed me as such,\\nDeputy Commissioner."
msgstr "No me dijo que hiciera eso,\\nSubcomisionado..."

msgctxt "2414	2491"
msgid "That won't do."
msgstr "Esto no va a funcionar."

msgctxt "2557	2600"
msgid "Listen."
msgstr "Mira."

msgctxt "2605	2755"
msgid "You're supposed to be helping me\\nbring about a new underground empire."
msgstr "Se supone que me estás ayudando\\na formar un nuevo imperio criminal."

msgctxt "2844	3087"
msgid "Letting a mountain of untraceable cash slip away...\\nSuch an amateur mistake is simply unacceptable."
msgstr "Cómo es posible que dejes escapar una montaña de dinero.\\nTal error es inaceptable."

msgctxt "3104	3296"
msgid "Use your head.\\nWe have nowhere near the funds we require."
msgstr "Usa tu cabeza.\\nObviamente necesitamos dinero para nuestros ideales."

msgctxt "3337	3424"
msgid "Surely that much is apparent even to you."
msgstr "Estoy seguro de que eso es evidente, incluso para ti."

msgctxt "3459	3519"
msgid "Yes, sir."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "3549	3609"
msgid "Good."
msgstr "Perfecto."

msgctxt "3768	3828"
msgid "I have to ask."
msgstr "Y bueno."

msgctxt "3836	3917"
msgid "Where is the money now?"
msgstr "¿Dónde está ese dinero ahora?"

msgctxt "3933	4069"
msgid "In the hands of Kazuma Kiryu\\nand his associates."
msgstr "En manos de Kazuma Kiryu\\ny sus asociados."

msgctxt "4083	4143"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr "Ya veo..."

msgctxt "4169	4282"
msgid "Then it'll be your responsibility\\nto retrieve it all from them."
msgstr "Entonces será tu responsabilidad\\nrecuperar esos 100 billones."

msgctxt "4293	4351"
msgid "How, sir?"
msgstr "¿Cómo?"

msgctxt "4356	4416"
msgid "We negotiate."
msgstr "Negociáremos."

msgctxt "4584	4697"
msgid "Even the toughest men have their weaknesses."
msgstr "Todo ser humano tiene una debilidad."

msgctxt "4745	4842"
msgid "Take these children from their home in Okinawa."
msgstr "Ve a Okinawa y trae a esos niños."

msgctxt "4895	5052"
msgid "With their lives on the line,\\nKiryu will surely come to the table."
msgstr "De esa manera,\\nese tal Kiryu debería aceptar el trato."

msgctxt "5373	5448"
msgid "Why the silence, Arai-kun?"
msgstr "¿Por qué no respondes, Arai-kun?"

msgctxt "5463	5566"
msgid "I thought this order\\nsimple enough even for you."
msgstr "Estoy seguro de que puedes\\ncumplir esta orden tan simple."

msgctxt "5618	5678"
msgid "It is, sir."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "5704	5870"
msgid "I don't expect you'll need it,\\nbut take this in case anyone gives you trouble."
msgstr "Si por casualidad tienes problemas,\\nusa esta pistola para contenerlos."

msgctxt "5871	5949"
msgid "It's nigh untraceable."
msgstr "Es imposible de rastrear."

msgctxt "6017	6077"
msgid "Good boy."
msgstr "¿Y bien?"

msgctxt "6205	6265"
msgid "Deputy Commissioner?"
msgstr "Subcomisionado."

msgctxt "6389	6449"
msgid "What are you...?"
msgstr "¡Tú...!"

msgctxt "6477	6613"
msgid "This is the end.\\nI'm done following orders."
msgstr "Se acabó.\\nYa no voy a seguir tus órdenes."

msgctxt "6629	6689"
msgid "Arai."
msgstr "Arai..."

msgctxt "6696	6768"
msgid "As a yakuza..."
msgstr "Como un yakuza..."

msgctxt "6784	6836"
msgid "No."
msgstr "No."

msgctxt "6841	6964"
msgid "As an officer of the law,\\nthere's a code I need to uphold."
msgstr "Como oficial de policía,\\nhay un código que debo seguir."

